cfr international spa
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Investment Companies
CFR International SpA operates as a holding company. The Company, through its subsidiaries, acquires and invests in related pharmaceutical companies on behalf of parent company. CFR International serves customers worldwide.




